            <thetext>I wish there were some type-specific cell renderers (one for Numbers, one for text, one for dates). That way, if you know you&#39;ll have the same type of data in your whole column, you can use those type-specific cell renderers and it will be faster (and the table widget needs all the speed improvements it can get as it&#39;s quite slow).

